{"tid":692793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(人性的考驗) 把200円放在日本公眾場所，一日後....","createTime":"2018-06-07T03:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T04:29:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":122,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"c347c297896e8276e4352cc8ccbe967a3a842cef","tid":692793,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/fun/talk/19/8180/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Ffun%2Ftalk%2F19%2F8180%2F&d=DMTlSmYv%2Fgz0sJvXWmeTxmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=982c4f93\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/fun/talk/19/8180/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔少人鍾意去日本旅行，原因之一係當地有好嘢食，有好嘢買，仲有靚景同溫泉，不過呢啲好處可能喺其他國家都搵得到，但好似日本治安咁好則未必度度都有。早前一名前往日本仙台出席會議嘅加拿大程式員 Godfrey Chan 就進行咗一個社會實驗，跳轉有片睇。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n    People say Japan is a very safe country. To put that to the test, I left &yen;200 in one of the most visible spots at the #rubykaigi venue yesterday.<br />\n<br />\n    Now there is &yen;300.<br />\n<br />\n    🤔 <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/lQAXNMi6Ly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FlQAXNMi6Ly&d=DMTlSmYv%2Fgz0sJvXWmeTxmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f90103b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/lQAXNMi6Ly</a><br />\n    &mdash; Godfrey Chan (@chancancode) 2018年6月2日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會議喺仙台國際中心舉行並且為期 3 日，Godfrey 為了體驗日本治安有幾好，於是諗到將兩個 100 日圓硬幣放在會場的一個藝術裝置上面。Godfrey 想知道有冇貪心嘅人會將銀仔取去，結果佢第二日再返到會場，藝術裝置上嘅兩個銀仔唔單止原封不動，而且更由 200 日圓變成 300 日圓，即係有人發現銀仔之餘，冇偷走到仲放多 100 日圓落去加碼。<br />\n<br />\n唔知 Godfrey 最後有冇拎走佢嗰 200 日圓，定係連人哋嗰 100 日圓都擸走埋呢？<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：chancancode<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fbc47456c0a5a6e81e341c436aa3e67380efac","tid":692793,"uid":26200,"like":409,"dislike":2,"score":407,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:27:13.000Z","msg":"應該係有人以為放落去祈福定咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{